Package: bareos-setup
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Backup Archiving Recovery Open Sourced - setup wizard
 Bareos is a set of programs to manage backup, recovery and verification of
 data across a network of computers of different kinds.
 .
 This package provides the bareos-setup wizard for initial Bareos
 configuration via a web-based interface.
